[30;1m87 | [0m[35m    """Decorator to assign extra deps for the plugin class.[0m
[30;1m88 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m89 | [0m[35m    There exist some plugins that cannot be executable with the default installation setup.[0m
[30;1m90 | [0m[35m    For example, `AcLauncher` plugin needs `tensorflow` and `openvino.tools` extra dependencies.[0m
